    <h2>What is Dip Report?</h2>
    <p>Dip Report is a free app built specifically for <strong>open water and sea swimmers in Ireland</strong>. Whether you swim at the Forty Foot in Sandycove, Seapoint, Killiney, Tramore, Portmarnock, or any of Ireland's hundreds of coastal spots, Dip Report gives you the information you actually need before you get in the water.</p>
    <p>Unlike generic weather apps, Dip Report combines <strong>wave height, swell direction, wind speed, tide levels, sea temperature, and rain probability</strong> into a single swimmer-focused view. No clutter, no irrelevant data ‚Äî just the conditions that matter for your dip.</p>
    <p>Available as a <strong>Progressive Web App (PWA)</strong> you can install directly to your home screen, and as a native <strong>Android app</strong>, Dip Report works seamlessly across all your devices.</p>
  </section>

