      <li><strong>Low Rain Only</strong> ‚Äî only notified when rain probability is under 10%</li>
      <li><strong>Forecast Offset</strong> ‚Äî get notified at 9am about conditions at 1pm (+4 hours)</li>
      <li><strong>Day Selection</strong> ‚Äî choose which days of the week each schedule applies to</li>
